Kompakt Records is a German record label, one of the most famous in the techno scene.
It is also a well-known distributor of electronic music (both vinyl and CD). Kompakt was founded in 1998 on the basis of the pre-existing labels Profan and Auftrieb. Kompakt Records is owned by Wolfgang Voigt, Michael Mayer and Jürgen Paape.
Several sublabels were founded on the label (Kompakt Extra, Kompakt Pop, Immer, K2, etc.).
Musicians such as Superpitcher, Justus Köhncke, GusGus, Tobias Thomas, The Modernist, DJ Koze and many others collaborate with the label.
